Join the Unapologetic Street Series on May 22 in Pomona, CA for a student-focused gathering centered on creativity, community, and collective action. Students will have the opportunity to connect with one another, explore public art and organizing as tools for change, and engage with local advocates and community resources. Free snacks, Plan C mini swag, and educational resources will be available, so be sure to stop by and pick up information about abortion pills by mail and reproductive health access.
